\ Dependencies
\ =============================================================================

REQUIRE %idir%/checks.vfx           \ Validations
REQUIRE %idir%/mode.vfx             \ Game modes w/ separate logic and rendering
REQUIRE %idir%/tweak.vfx            \ Persistent variable control
REQUIRE %idir%/waveplay.vfx         \ Audio engine
REQUIRE %idir%/utilities.vfx        \ Math helpers, audio, and misc utilities
REQUIRE %idir%/traits.vfx           \ Object traits
REQUIRE %idir%/asset.vfx            \ Base asset class
REQUIRE %idir%/shader.vfx           \ Shaders 
REQUIRE %idir%/crt.vfx              \ CRT shader

